{"tid":1154252,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"學生資助係咪on9","createTime":"2019-05-14T07:05:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T08:46:20.000Z","uid":113360,"like":1,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4e475cda265fac578ad514dd21afe6d464b55dbf","tid":1154252,"uid":113360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T07:05:20.000Z","msg":"小弟家貧 來年都仲要申請學生資助<br />\n上年用過一排支那寶chok啲優惠卷所以銀行轉賬交易比較多，但都係啲小數目<br />\n<br />\n前幾日學生資助處個邊黎咗封信話要我交Alipay係3月31號嘅戶口結餘同上年度嘅交易記錄。<br />\n<br />\n但我冇係3月31號個日 cap低戶口結餘。就算有，佢個app都冇日期時間同個人資料可以同時show出黎。頭先打咗個電話去問，點知負責人請咗病假到下星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，改咗比個老嘢聽，個老嘢擺明都唔識呢啲嘢，只係不斷複述要同時show資料黎證明係我戶口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打絲打都遇過呢種情況，可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eff434fe1d904054630b4d460117909c12aba965","tid":1154252,"uid":191453,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T07:06:52.000Z","msg":"抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0026804a77a5152faab080aecc327015f96ed298","tid":1154252,"uid":28800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T07:08:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"29a774ebe0e64b9139af1c5d78c2b945abc0d611","tid":1154252,"uid":11311,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T07:10:05.000Z","msg":"用支那野抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"600f2821a80fdfa812b9e5b716a92598aa759b79","tid":1154252,"uid":113360,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"0026804a77a5152faab080aecc327015f96ed298","tid":1154252,"uid":28800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T07:08:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T07:12:38.000Z","msg":"個app係冇得同時show埋戶口結餘同今日日期<br />\n同埋證明唔到個交易記錄係我嘅<br />\n<br />\n佢亦都冇電腦版可以詳細列印"},{"pid":"b542aa92e7a874ecadebd6d2e2e74a7c0285137a","tid":1154252,"uid":72186,"li